original: Åberg, Johan Olof Tage, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 24/6/07 i Sthlm av käll:-mäst. Johan A. o. Ellen Rehn. G. 36 m. Anna-Lisa Karlsson. — Stud:ex. i Örebro 27, Cand. med. dent. i Rostock 31, tysk tandläk. i Bonn 32, svensk tandlläk. 34. Prakt, i Trollhättan 37-46, egen prakt, i Mölndal sed. 46.
translated: Åberg, Johan Olof Tage, dentist, Gothenburg, b. 24/6/07 in Stockholm to pewter master Johan A. and Ellen Rehn. Married for 36 years to Anna-Lisa Karlsson. - Completed high school exams in Örebro in '27, obtained a dental medicine degree in Rostock in '31, worked as a German dentist in Bonn in '32, and as a Swedish dentist in '34. Practiced in Trollhättan from '37-'46 and established his own practice in Mölndal since '46.
